  "Description": [
    "extensions to the C++ standard library Abseil is an open-source collection of C++ library code designed to augment the C++ standard library. The Abseil library code is collected from Google's C++ codebase and has been extensively tested and used in production. In some cases, Abseil provides pieces missing from the C++ standard; in others, Abseil provides alternatives to the standard for special needs."
